exceptions.exn: Unable to apply lemma of type "forall (m : fmap) (k : dim) (z : dart), inv_hmap m -> ~ exd m z -> A_1 m k z = nil" on hypothesis of type "A_1 m one (A_1 m zero z) = nil".

original: intros m z Hinv. split. - intros Hsucc. unfold F. destruct Hsucc as [Hpred1 Hpred2]. intro Hnil. apply not_exd_A_1_nil in Hnil. 2: { apply cA_1_exd with (k := one). apply Hinv. auto. } apply (succ_pred_clos m zero z) in Hinv as [Hc1 _]. unfold pred in Hpred1. unfold F in Hpred2. specialize (Hc1 Hpred1). specialize (Hnil Hpred2). unfold cA in Hc1, Hnil. rewrite Hnil in Hc1. contradiction. - intros HF. unfold F in HF. split. + assert (contra := not_exd_A_1_nil m one (A_1 m zero z)). destruct (succf_dec m z). * apply succf_exd_F in s as Hexd. apply cA_1_exd with (k := zero) in HF as Hexd_f. apply Hinv. contradiction. * destruct (not_exd_cA_1 m zero z Hinv n) as Hcontra. symmetry. apply Hcontra. + assert (contra := not_exd_A_1_nil m zero (A_1 m one (A_1 m zero z))). destruct (succf_dec m (A_1 m zero z)). * apply succf_exd_F with (z := A_1 m zero z) in s as Hexd. apply cA_exd with (k := one) in HF as Hexd_f. apply Hinv. contradiction. * destruct (not_exd_cA_1 m one (A_1 m zero z) Hinv n) as Hcontra. symmetry. apply Hcontra.
